        a different program (whose header we have included). We need to access
        it via the specific offset within that header's schema includes.
        We add 1 to the include's index, since we always place the program
        itself at position 0, with includes at positions 1 onwards. }}
    {{#let prog=include.schema_provider_program}}
readSchemaInclude(::{{prog.cpp_qualified_namespace}}::{{prog.name}}_constants
::{{prog.schema_name}}_includes, {{(int.add 1 include.schema_index)}})
